Package org.wikidata.wdtk.datamodel.json.jackson.datavalues Description

Jackson-compatible implementation of all WDTK Value interfaces for use as snak values. The JSON serializations typically differ even for values that occur in other places too, hence separate implementations are required.
Author:
Fredo Erxleben
